    <string-array name="introscreen_summaries">
        <item>Welcome to Smooth Clicker!</item>
        <item>You need to have a rooted Android device to use this app.</item>
        <item>Define several clicks to process… </item>
        <item>… and configure the process with notifications, vibrations etc.</item>
        <item>Some JSON files can be used to store the configuration of the click process.</item>
        <item>The standalone mode can start the click process using only the JSON configuration files.</item>
        <item>The standalone mode can also start the click process according to a picture of the screen.</item>
        <item>Smooth Clicker is both free and open-source!</item>
    </string-array>
